high_descs: Walk over to the counter to the left of the oven and look up.
Open the upper cabinet to the left of the microwave and remove the sponge, then close the cabinet.
Turn around and walk towards the wall, then hang a left and walk towards the counter, turn left to face the oven.
Put the sponge in the brass pot that is on the front left burner of the stove.
Pick up the brass pot with the sponge in it off of the stove.
Turn around and walk over to the wall, then hang a right and walk up to the wall, turn right again to face the white table.
Put the brass pot with the sponge in it on the white table.
anns.task_desc: Put a brass pot with a sponge in it on a white table.

high_descs: Walk forwards to the white cabinet in front of you.
Open up the white cabinet and take out the sponge from in the cabinet.
Turn around and walk to your right, and then turn right again to the kitchen stove.
Set the sponge down into the large pot on the stove-top.
Pick up the large pot while the sponge is in the pot.
Turn around, walk forwards, turn to your right, and then right again to the white table.
Set the pot with the sponge inside down on the left side of the white table.
anns.task_desc: Set down a pot with a sponge inside on the white kitchen table.

high_descs: go forward to upper cabinet to the left of stove
open upper cabinet, pick up green sponge from cabinet, close cabinet
go to stove to the right
place green sponge in large pot on front left burner of stove
pick up pot with green sponge from stove
turn around, go to left end of white table by small wood stool
place pot with green sponge on table by wood stool
anns.task_desc: place pot with green sponge on table by wood stool
